{"tid":1873513,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"新手9 wu 露營谷","createTime":"2020-02-10T16:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T23:42:10.000Z","uid":103531,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"058100dd6a921cdeb15607a01e142d9dec47939f","tid":1873513,"uid":103531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打絲打係想去下露營玩下但又唔知要入手d咩 / 想去但又冇朋友陪<br />\n<br />\n我地呢個谷有新手有老手<br />\n成班都係鐘意hea下吹水之人<br />\n基本上10至4月前都會每月一團 (星期六日)<br />\n基於新手較新同老手年紀大關係<br />\n通常都會去一啲交通方便既營地 (有日出日落既就更好)<br />\n除左普通露營，咁我地都會喺煮食方面搞下新意<br />\n好似玩下紙箱雞同炭燒煲仔飯<br />\n只要你符合以下條件又有興趣就可以入<br />\n<br />\n1.肯課下金 - 咁基本營具架生(營,地𥱊,睡袋)你冇都要課下金既 (會有落坑團同大家一齊課金，平有平玩貴有貴玩，任君選擇)，同埋預左大家夾錢一齊煮野食 <br />\n2.唔係獨家村，肯成班一齊玩下吹下水既。<br />\n3.黃絲限定，藍絲你自己死返出去啦，無你既事<br />\n4.古語有云，露營必須酒，谷友們都喜歡淺酌幾杯，如果大家不抗拒酒精就最好<br />\n5.本谷只歡迎心境成年既朋友入谷，絕不對黃腔設立任何限制，大家自律便可。如有對他人過份冒犯之意，即踢免問。厹公娘娘可以唔洗入谷了。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既巴絲，條link喺下面<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/IisX0BIXQ2ZsgIZ4UjfcfA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FIisX0BIXQ2ZsgIZ4UjfcfA&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4W7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=f8e4ca30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/IisX0BIXQ2ZsgIZ4UjfcfA</a><br />\n<br />\n一齊玩下啦!"},{"pid":"b1b1f237f01310be15d422a5e176f763fcfff9f0","tid":1873513,"uid":14169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eoJT5Kx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeoJT5Kx.jpg&h=cbd8f543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紙箱雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7b61560ee6e226e92d0ce5baba38021a3abd91","tid":1873513,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"露營地啲廁所通常好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打點睇"},{"pid":"35a7677e49e5beaaccc3577eaf3d7ba92fa75fb3","tid":1873513,"uid":103531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b7b61560ee6e226e92d0ce5baba38021a3abd91","tid":1873513,"uid":78374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"露營地啲廁所通常好污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打點睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T23:48:02.000Z","msg":"一兩日冇乜所謂既<br />\n又唔係叫你長住<br />\n<br />\n不過我地就盡量揀d有靚厠所既營地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4651636fb4a9ece19017225854f6a50ba1a67dbf","tid":1873513,"uid":257539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"係日本玩既可唔可以join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fmRyoxS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfmRyoxS.png&h=f0f2a089&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68583701d11905c8aa8449faac786751edd8b0a0","tid":1873513,"uid":103531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4651636fb4a9ece19017225854f6a50ba1a67dbf","tid":1873513,"uid":257539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T23:49:57.000Z","msg":"係日本玩既可唔可以join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fmRyoxS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfmRyoxS.png&h=f0f2a089&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"Why not<br />\n交流下"},{"pid":"6f0c717a29a5f1abbe051cbbc2d9a16aa768cb2d","tid":1873513,"uid":14169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T06:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded8e5a7c7135a71e8d6f9637dba3d92552ed1b2","tid":1873513,"uid":33050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"Lm 學野"},{"pid":"8667016f0e70650ff9b82f4d31cb94925d6bd813","tid":1873513,"uid":272614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b7b61560ee6e226e92d0ce5bab